description: Folks of Columbus are starting their day the tasty way, thanks to The Cluckwagon!After gaining a foodie following at Old Worthington Farmers Market, this team is now taking their delicious chicken breakfast dishes through town in their brand new plucky truck. They're serving up scrumptious Sammies with chicken breakfast sausage, cheese, and egg- fried golden and crispy, and served on a variety of breads, including glazed donuts. For all this and more, be sure to come out and try the best cluck for your buck!
name: The Cluckwagon
